<!-- May 2016 - Add DefinitionEnOnly and DefinitionFrOnly to the Text element  
	before: <!ENTITY % inline  "(#PCDATA | Ins | Sub | Sup | Emphasis
                     | DefinedTermEn | DefinedTermFr | FootnoteRef 
                     | Language | Leader | LeaderRightJustified | XRefInternal 
                     | XRefExternal | PageBreak | Keep | ImageGroup | Fraction )*" >
	now: <!ENTITY % inline  "(#PCDATA | Ins | Sub | Sup | Emphasis
